<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>今天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就跟着日报君去瞧一瞧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都有哪些厦门元素</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>厦门金鼎巷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧中李尖尖爸爸经营的<strong>“海潮面馆”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出镜率很高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/213a6f34c0894d07ba3a5114f751d80f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/7dd87ca5896e44d898c568e995121be8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧中不同年代的面馆外观</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">网友认出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面馆实地就<strong>位于厦门金鼎巷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在东渡商检站附近</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/a54b79bf95664ce48f6ed5d6f5209a49.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">多位周边居民向日报君指出，图中就是当时面馆的拍摄地。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/d1d51190181f4225ac458f7066eb61d9.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">金鼎巷</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>华新路</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧中三兄妹上下学常走的路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就在<strong>华新路</strong>附近</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/732993c98848413f8e9fc7dc29cef7e0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/dde107155c9f4187998c1db72f1a0093.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧中的小路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">华新路是一条极具文艺气息的道路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">建筑和店铺都十分有特色</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/6439fcf20c2046fb852e9dbeed2dfa71.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>杏林湾商务营运中心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主角们经常散步、聊天的场景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就发生在<strong>杏林湾商务营运中心附近</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/57fb03e39d264879bc195e4898c32270.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/6b66d197a1fe4e5f921755db54ebead9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧中场景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/270ca0f10b1b437e85795d0e7e06b337.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">杏林湾商务营运中心附近（图片来源于天下集美）</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>莲花新城公交车站</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三兄妹常等车的公交车站车站</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">位于<strong>莲花新城站</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以看到他们乘坐的是<strong>947路</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/59f523dbc6cf4b078beb52c6fe80ec87.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/a82327cfd7994e70809e8e46af057aa6.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">剧中的公交车站和公交车</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/b804f2e2dc3f424eacb8357d53f2aae7.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">莲花新城站（来源百度地图全景）</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>海沧体育中心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贺子秋和小伙伴经常打篮球的地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是<strong>海沧体育中心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1346ed51bffd48028dc1ef26bca8d859.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/e4c5e97245b4421e9913fd3e053528ef.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">剧中的篮球场</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/f977cab1c1c942ed8455a7d2878451f1.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">海沧体育中心（来源百度地图全景）</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>海沧大桥＆狐尾山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三兄妹家的天台</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以清楚地看到远处的<strong>海沧大桥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和<strong>狐尾山</strong>上的海上明珠塔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/e9eb61ac5a544f90894791bea1140f51.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">剧中的天台</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8f014b96faa347e7828b06e8ef9e22d1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/0f91d7afd6654deebb82a25b332cf9e8.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">海沧大桥</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/30c4b6ee2208493189619e288a5c75ed.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">狐尾山海上明珠塔</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这些地方你认出了吗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧中不时出现的城市风光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都让人一眼认出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就是<strong>厦门</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/434810bb571e4dc789709e65623de6a0.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">中山路片区附近，可以看到远处的海关钟楼、第一广场等建筑。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/04260fc0813e4108b75adaa8c687a17a.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">民族路周边。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8144a21a516c4b78af291f4db1b2a33d.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">软件园三期。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1aac0a6d3d44466ca809ba6b55c638a9.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">厦大及演武大桥附近。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/9f3c074d9eb84f14a5987e47a462af09.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">李尖尖写生的地点位于海沧湾公园。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/616933e363494e9d822c5f4d78d5d738.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">闺蜜相聚的地方应该是万象城外。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/7a9c11a2708f446e8a1beda98787e0a1.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">筼筜湖夜景。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还有这些厦门元素</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>闽D车牌</strong>在剧中随处可见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1e9403beca5745bb886ef373b25f33da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧中李尖尖家里铺的<strong>花砖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是许多老厦门人家里的常见装饰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/3dd8a70f7266499d8df1bb64e19518c1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李尖尖爸爸李海潮的<strong>荣誉证书</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也能看到“厦门”字样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/66a75991933744fc9dc4561693f453d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">救护车车身上写着<strong>“厦门急救”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/a6374167a7c240cdb235d1dcfbdafe1c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面馆的柜台里摆着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">厦门人熟悉的<strong>丹凤高粱酒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/ededdc6aedb141328e4cfcd6bf796498.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有小伙伴认为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小凌霄自己泡的面应该是<strong>厦门泡面</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/b88538521e2942bf9f88a9fdecedb881.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
